Name: 3-3 Driven by Instinct
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked monsters\nOperation Portal was run by Strike Hawk. After joining forces with them, Gray Raven was assigned the task of scouting in the Estate where the portal was located.

Name: 3-4 Good Samaritan
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nHassen gave you a priority mission. Before joining Strike Hawk, you need to retrieve the Constructs in the subway station with Gray Raven.

Name: 3-5 Trespassing
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nTifa was also one of the "new variants." How the Corrupted suddenly gained the ability to think was still unknown, but they quickly occupied the subway station after she was gone.

Name: 3-6 Traps
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nThe Corrupted significantly impacted the retrieval of Constructs. Gray Raven decided to split into two groups; one would continue working on the retrieval, while the other would focus on fighting the Corrupted.

Name: 3-7 Final Warning
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nOperation Portal was run by Strike Hawk. After joining forces with them, Gray Raven was assigned the task of scouting in the Estate where the portal was located.

Name: 3-8 Take Caution
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nAfter scouting, Gray Raven's next task is night patrol.

Name: 3-10 A Twisted Hobby
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nOperation Portal is about to start. Gray Raven and Strike Hawk will launch a joint attack on the Estate.

Name: 3-11 Loyalty
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nA new variant, along with many Corrupted reinforcements, suddenly appeared in the Estate. Defeat the new variant and evacuate ASAP.

Name: 3-12 A New Seed
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nThe operation has started again. Gray Raven will distract the enemy so Strike Hawk can infiltrate the Estate.

Name: 4-1 Night Escape
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nTo attract as much firepower as possible, Gray Raven decided to enter the Estate building.

Name: 4-2 Elimination
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nFor some unknown reason, Gray Raven lost contact with Strike Hawk. The priority now is to get out of this place.

Name: 4-3 Broken Chain
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nStrike Hawk suffered a heavy loss, so Kamui was reassigned to Gray Raven, whose last task here is to establish a safe zone.

Name: 4-4 Zack
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nCover Lee so he could set up the Iso-Device outside the Estate and hence establish a safe route between the base and the portal.

Name: 4-5 Raging Sand
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nA siren suddenly went off in the Estate. Check it out and ensure the portal is safe.

Name: 4-6 Panic Dive
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nTurned out it was some Corrupted that triggered the safety robots. Destroy the Corrupted and the robots.

Name: 4-7 Forsaken
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nThe portal was tampered by Roland and failed to send you to the designated location. After some discussion, you decided to walk there.

Name: 4-8 Reinforcement
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nKamui seemed to have this desert's information. Gray Raven headed toward the desert base for supplies and Construct maintenance.

Name: 4-9 None Shall Pass
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nGray Raven was met with some uninvited guests who called themselves the "Forsaken", and was attacked by one of the male Constructs.

Name: 4-10 Silent Night
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nThe desert base was under attack of the Corrupted. Defeat them to protect the base.

Name: 4-11 Noises
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nThe "Forsaken" Constructs seemed to know Lucia and Kamui. Gray Raven set off once again to seize the base and find out the truth.

Name: 4-12 Battle in Temple
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nThe mysterious Construct who clearly disliked humans appeared again. He was upset by Gray Raven as they were taking orders from you. A battle is imminent.

Name: Camu
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nThe male Construct took advantage of the Corrupted's habits and got them to attack Gray Raven. Lucia seemed to have recalled something during the battle though...?

Name: Riot
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nFight with overclocked enemies\nThe enemy Construct's name was Watanabe. But before Lucia could recall more, a type of enemy named "Shieldbearer" started to attack...

Name: Wispthorn
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nNo one knew what Luna was thinking when she made herself this Coating. The glowing thorns entangled her like everlasting shackles. "May the apostates burn in the fire of these thorns."

Name: Florescence
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nShe quietly awaits, like a blooming bud that awaits to be picked up, hoping that her feelings would one day be discovered.

Name: Grace
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\nShe had witnessed many lives stepping into the divine hall. Never had she thought that one day that she could wear this outfit herself, as you took her hand in the blessed light.

Name: Scarlet Spring
SingleDescription:
No Stamina cost

When spring returns to the garden, flowers would blossom brilliantly.
The elegant pattern is made from a traditional gold-weaving technique.
Qu does not have many opportunities to wear this outfit, but she still hopes this indispensable part of Tabula Akasha can be shown to the world.

Name: Azure Apocalypse
SingleDescription:
No Stamina cost

Finally, it is over, and all the noises in the world come to a screeching halt.
She returns to you, freed from all the thorns brought by the fate.
You have each other for all the time from now on.

Name: Howling Crown
SingleDescription:
No Stamina cost

When all things are silent, she still holds the shining spear up high.
For she vows to protect, save, and uphold this world with dignity.
You are the first to discover her in the snow.

Name: Honor Model
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nThe custom-made uniform of the outstanding graduates of F.O.S. It is close-fitting but does not impede movement, flashy but not ostentatious, suitable for attending various occasions. The pure gold chain presiding on the chest always reminds the dresser to shoulder the mission of the elite, to hang the honor and responsibility on the heart, and to become a glorious example to lead the crowd.

Name: Street Rebellion
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nWith young and frivolous as the main concept of the design, the coating shows the rebellion and self of the lone wolf girl. Just standing at the corner of the street in this dress, it seems that it can release an aura that strangers are not allowed to approach.

Name: Nosferatu
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nHe drinks up a glass of redness in the dark night in the song of praise sung by all beings. Although unable to embrace the light, he would still guard you silently in the darkness.

Name: Deed of Snow Leopard
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\n\n"What can I do for you, Commandant...? Wait! Why do I have to do this?" Although there is anger in the girl's eyes, she will only bare her fangs when she tries to protect her allies. She will also try her best to temporarily disguise herself for missions. And of course, she won't let anyone take her most important customer away from her.

Name: Spring Huntress
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nInspired by a royal spring hunting tradition thousands of years ago, this coating combines the traditional archer costume with the aristocratic clothing style. It dispels misfortune and misery that imprison the world with the sound of the deities and brings back spring.

Name: Tiger Imperium
SingleDescription: No Stamina Cost\n\nA tiger general charges onto the battlefield, slashing at the enemies with his greatsword. To fit the user's untamed style, this new coating is designed with various wild animal patterns that seem to carry the power of a mythical oriental beast, making the user look even fiercer.

Name: Illusionist
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost.\n\nThe magician hides the special gift he prepared in advance with magic and pulls out a red heart with a brilliant magic skill. Even though the audience is already impressed, the magician's eyes are only fixed on only one of them. Now, he has put the response in your hand.

Name: Dreamweaver
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost.\n\nA Coating made based on Pulao's description of her dream. With great passion, Pulao described the tea room waiters, the old man who sold prune drinks, and the shop owner who recommended her this suit. "Char siu buns are the best!" "You look like an idol in this suit!" These sentences always echo in everyone's M.I.N.D. after Pulao's passionate interpretation.

Name: Wavebender
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\n\nShe has reduced her armor to the minimum to make sure that she can surf freely in the feast of music. However, what interests her more is to lie under a sunshade and watch how helpless you are until she calls you when the time's right, "Commandant, get that for me." As a reward, she will share the small space under her sunshade with you.

Name: Exorcist
SingleDescription: No Stamina cost\n\nThe exorcist's lamp shines bright before her chest with her silver blade reflecting her beautiful face. With her golden eyes fixed on the shadow of the past, she will eventually find out the truth at the end of the dark realm.
